<paragraph blockId="48.[151,1436,1462,2026]" pageId="48" pageNumber="49">
Antenna 1 (
<figureCitation box="[329,412,1462,1486]" captionStart="FIGURE 36" captionStartId="49.[151,250,1982,2005]" captionTargetBox="[179,1369,200,1940]" captionTargetId="figure-49@49.[179,1403,193,1948]" captionTargetPageId="49" captionText="FIGURE 36. Leucon (M.) weigmanni sp. n., A1: antenna 1, Mxp2: maxilliped 2, Mxp3: maxilliped 3, P1: pereiopod 1, P2: pereiopod 2; scale bars: 100 µm (A1, Mxp2, Mxp3) and 200 µm (P1, P2)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5246223" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5246223/files/figure.png" pageId="48" pageNumber="49">Fig. 36</figureCitation>
